flowchart TD
    A[Start run &#40;user_query&#41;] --> B[Reset loop_count = 0]
    B --> C[Build messages: system prompt + few-shot + user query]
    C --> D{loop_count < max_loops?}

    D -- No --> Z[Print: Limit of reasoning 5 loops complete<br/>Return Final_Uncertain]
    D -- Yes --> E[Increment loop_count]
    E --> F[Call LLM chat.completions.create]
    F --> G[Get output text]
    G --> H[Print output]

    H --> I{Contains Final: or Final_Uncertain:?}
    I -- Yes --> J[Return output]
    I -- No --> K{Contains Action:?}

    K -- No --> L[Append repair message:<br/>You must follow Thought → Action format]
    L --> D

    K -- Yes --> M[Parse Action line]
    M --> N{Parse success?}

    N -- No --> O[Append repair message:<br/>Malformed Action. Use Search&#91;...&#93;]
    O --> D

    N -- Yes --> P[Extract search query]
    P --> Q[Execute search&#40;query&#41;]
    Q --> R{Observation empty?}

    R -- Yes --> S[Set observation = No results found.]
    R -- No --> T[Keep returned observation]

    S --> U[Print Observation]
    T --> U

    U --> V[Append assistant output to messages]
    V --> W[Append user Observation to messages]
    W --> D